<item>
            <title>[LU-10750] mdd_close() should check if changelogs are enabled</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10750</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the normal path of &lt;tt&gt;mdd_close()&lt;/tt&gt; we create a transaction and declare a changelog record for close even if changelogs are disabled.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are also several places where we declare changelog records that may not be created depending on the changelog mask.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
